title: Star Wars Jedi Quest fix
description:
Looks like I made a small mistake in my previous torrent.

The &#039;Jedi Quest&#039; .rar files contained some double files.

I removed these bringing the size for all 4 files down from 918 to 482mb.

Part 1 of the Jedi Quest series also contained some strange noises at the end of most files and a short sample of a song by the British girl group &#039;Sugababes&#039; at the end of file 6. (Imagine the look on my face when I heard that for the first time)

My idea is that this all occurred when the original ripper copied the audio books from a cassette player deck to a computer. The strange noises sound a lot like cassette players make, and the &#039;Sugababes sample&#039; is probably due to him pressing the tuner button which mixed in some live radio.

I removed all of this for this torrent. You can remove the double files yourself if you already downloaded the Jedi Quest audio books from the previous torrent and the strange noises and Sugababes sample aren&#039;t any real distraction.



The next Era, &#039;Rebellion Era&#039;, coming soon!



I suggest that you bookmark my account http://thepiratebay.se/user/Starkiller20/ to stay up-to-date!!!
